The planet of love, beauty, cooperation, and material pleasures, Venus is often a makeup artists favorite planet ğŸ¥° 

Venus in astrology embodies all things of love and beauty. Venus symbolizes our love language and how we give and receive love. It symbolizes all of our partnerships, including relationships, business, and every area of life where we cooperate with another. Venus shows our love (or disdain) of material pleasures, and can show (along with midheaven/10th house) how we can best earn our money. Those with a strong sense of aesthetics and beauty typically have an exalted, domicile, or well aspected Venus placement in their chart. However, a Venus that is challenged or otherwise afflicted can symbolize troubles with love and finances.
